         <!---marked by line number? Editor's notes (non corrections) here? --->
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <p>To the Shades of the Underworld. Faustina (made this) for her most dear and well-deserving husband Primiti[v]us, who was in his forieth year of life (?), with whom she lived twelve years , eight months, seven days; and also Felix and Maximinus, students (?), made this for their well-deserving teacher.</p>
            <ab/></ab>
         </div>
